steps.name: And  the user is on the login page
And  the user clicks the login button
Then  the user should be logged in and directed to the dashboard
When  the admin clicks the admin button
And  the admin clicks the add-user button AdminPage
And  the admin selects the user role and enters employee name "Random"
And  the admin selects the status and enters username "Random"
And  the admin enters password "Random" and confirm password "Random"
Then  on clicking the add user button the admin should be able to add a user
